messages.messageBody:
-=-Ohhhh I so miss animaniacs and pinky and the brain . :) -=-

Here, have some:
http://sandradodd.com/history/songs

I added "The Meticulous Analysis of History," a fine Pinky and the
Brain song. You'll have to click it to play it (with apologies to
those on dial-up; never mind). The link on the right will go to
lyrics and links to videos.

Both Season 1 of Animaniacs and a Pinky and the Brain collection are
out on DVD.

Sandra
